com.radinfodesign.fboace

Class FBOAce

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radinfodesign.fboace.FBOAce

  • public class FBOAce
extends java.lang.Object
    This class only exists to provide an overview document for the package fboace and its sub-packages and classes.

    This is a Demo generated application; YOUR app will be something else, but with a similar (sub-)package structure: controller, dao (Repository), model (data entities) and service.
    All of the sub-packages and their classes are optional except for those under model; these are the classes from which all the others are generated. Please note that your application.properties file must include a valid database connection string and credentials to the schema that your model entities represent; some of the finer-grained attributes needed by RADSpringBootGen are only available from database metadata (views USER_TABLES, USER_TAB_COLUMNS etc).
    All generated artifacts will eventually be exported to a separate project and application, but during the generation and validation process it may be convenient to integrate them here, effectively conjoining your app under development with the code generation framework during a short period, after which they may all be exported and deleted from here.
    Get used to rebuilding and relaunching the RADSpringBootGenApplication several times during your generation and validation process.
